# Instructions

* Make sure "Features" module is added to the site and enabled.
* Enable the "Carriers" feature module.
* Go to admin/structure/features and enable the feature.
* If the comments module is turned on, go to admin/structure/types/manage/carrier and set comments to hidden.
* Create a new page called "Carriers".
* Add the Carrier blocks to the newly created page.
* Add the new page to the "Useful Resources" menu.

